_source.text: 10. Life in Southeast Asia in the seventeenth century was probably better than it was in other parts of Asia during the same time period because: (Points: 5) the region had a very cool climate.

text: 10. Life in **Southeast** **Asia** in the seventeenth century was probably **better** **than** it was in other
parts of Asia during the same time period because: (Points: 5) the **region** had a very cool climate.
